    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You make sure every fight has some flare in it. At 11th level, when you cast a Tojo clan Hijutsu, you may spend 3 EX Die to cast a jutsu that requires stance as an action or bonus action. When you do this, if the stance requires to be used as a finisher, you may use it regardless. If the jutsu has a special effect that only activates due to a feature from your stance, that effect activates even if the prerequisite is not fulfilled</p>",
